&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Your Role: &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Community Operations Intern will support day-to-day community operations across WeChat, Discord, and Xiaohongshu, keeping the community active and engaged. This role plays a key part in planning and executing community events, creating engaging content, and turning user feedback into actionable insights. The ideal candidate is empathetic, highly organized, and execution-driven.&lt;/p&gt;
