&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Event Operations:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Plan and execute hackathons, tech talks, and developer meetups end-to-end, from program design and promotion to on-site execution and retrospectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Creation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Create community content and campaign copy; curate high-quality user-generated content (UGC).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Insights &amp;amp; Reporting:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Gather user feedback, deliver weekly community metrics reports, and nurture key opinion consumers (KOCs).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Basic Qualifications:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
