&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Strong writing skills and fluency with major social platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry Knowledge:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Solid understanding of the North American humanoid robotics industry (e.g., Tesla Optimus, Figure, 1X) and the Web3 space — community culture, DAO governance, and common playbooks such as airdrops, whitelists, and NFT communities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Style:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Empathetic, highly organized, and execution-driven.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience running social accounts or communities is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
