&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Data-Driven Growth Specialist will join Faraday Future&#39;s Content Commerce Center, owning the full data-to-revenue path across GEO search authority, paid digital marketing and performance media, full-funnel conversion, and AI-powered growth automation. This role is responsible for turning every traffic source — paid digital, organic, social, and LLM-driven — into measurable qualified leads and revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a builder role, not a manager role. The Specialist operates as a high-leverage growth function — designing systems, shipping automations, and compounding AI-augmented workflows rather than coordinating headcount. The bar is leverage, not scale of team. Every manual task done twice becomes an automation; every automation compounds into FF&#39;s growth operating system.&lt;/p&gt;
