&lt;li&gt;Follow traffic laws and ensure a professional experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use company-provided navigation tools for seamless trips.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Will need to travel occasionally between HQ and Manufacturing Plant in Hanford, CA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure cleanliness and routine maintenance check of vehicles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Basic Qualifications:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or GED required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A valid California Driver License with at least 5 years of clean driving record.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be at least 25 years old (for insurance purposes)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional, good communication and customer service skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in driving automatic transmission vehicles; manual transmission experience is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Advanced Driver Assistance Systems (ADAS) and Autonomous Driving Systems (ADS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with new vehicle features and functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to operate small handheld tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with MS Teams, Word, Excel, PowerPoint and Outlook&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is a safety-sensitive position, must be able to pass pre-employment background and drug testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible to work evenings, weekend or overtime as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lift 50 pounds, sit for long drive, squat, stoop, climb ladders, and carry materials and tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ride share experience is plus&lt;/li&gt;
